room_title: Escape room "Mayday" by Escape Plan Nashville in Nashville
room_description: The excitement you felt after you and your team finally found the elusive Fenn treasure, hidden deep in the Rocky Mountains, quickly vanishes as you awake on the flight home to find you and your team have been drugged and are secured to your seat. With the plane in flight and no response from the cockpit, the race is on to free yourselves, find out what has happened, and most importantly, get back to the ground safely!
